{"tha-ap496:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap496:0.2":"Kinkanipupphavagga ","tha-ap496:0.3":"Kimsukapupphiyattheraapadana ","tha-ap496:1.1":"“Kimsukam pupphitam disva, ","tha-ap496:1.2":"paggahetvana anjalim; ","tha-ap496:1.3":"Buddhasettham saritvana, ","tha-ap496:1.4":"akase abhipujayim. ","tha-ap496:2.1":"Tena kammena sukatena, ","tha-ap496:2.2":"cetanapanidhihi ca; ","tha-ap496:2.3":"Jahitva manusam deham, ","tha-ap496:2.4":"tavatimsamagacchaham. ","tha-ap496:3.1":"Ekatimse ito kappe, ","tha-ap496:3.2":"yam kammamakarim tada; ","tha-ap496:3.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap496:3.4":"buddhapujayidam phalam. ","tha-ap496:4.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap496:4.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap496:4.3":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap496:5.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","tha-ap496:5.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap496:5.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap496:6.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap496:6.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap496:6.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap496:7.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma kimsukapupphiyo thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap496:8.1":"Kimsukapupphiyattherassapadanam catuttham. "}